br.com.lett.crawlernode.queue

Class QueueService

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.lett.crawlernode.queue.QueueService

  • public class QueueService
extends java.lang.Object
    A bridge with the Amazon SQS. The other crawlers modules uses the methods from this class to send messages, do requests and delete messages from the queue. The long pooling time is sort of in sync with the Timer thread on the main method in class Main. This time is the time that a request on the queue waits until some message is on the request response.
    Author:
    Samir Leao
